{"name":"Lean.Elab.InfoTree","instances":[{"typeNames":["Lean.Elab.ContextInfo"],"name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedContextInfo","className":"Inhabited"},{"typeNames":["Lean.Elab.ElabInfo"],"name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedElabInfo","className":"Inhabited"},{"typeNames":["Lean.Elab.TermInfo"],"name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedTermInfo","className":"Inhabited"},{"typeNames":["Lean.Elab.CommandInfo"],"name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedCommandInfo","className":"Inhabited"},{"typeNames":["Lean.Elab.FieldInfo"],"name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedFieldInfo","className":"Inhabited"},{"typeNames":["Lean.Elab.TacticInfo"],"name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedTacticInfo","className":"Inhabited"},{"typeNames":["Lean.Elab.MacroExpansionInfo"],"name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedMacroExpansionInfo","className":"Inhabited"},{"typeNames":["Lean.Elab.CustomInfo"],"name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedCustomInfo","className":"Inhabited"},{"typeNames":["Lean.Elab.CustomInfo"],"name":"Lean.Elab.instToFormatCustomInfo","className":"Std.ToFormat"},{"typeNames":["Lean.Elab.Info"],"name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedInfo","className":"Inhabited"},{"typeNames":["Lean.Elab.InfoTree"],"name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedInfoTree","className":"Inhabited"},{"typeNames":["Lean.Elab.InfoState"],"name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedInfoState","className":"Inhabited"},{"typeNames":[],"name":"Lean.Elab.instMonadInfoTree","className":"Lean.Elab.MonadInfoTree"}],"imports":["Init","Lean.Data.Position","Lean.Expr","Lean.Message","Lean.Data.Json","Lean.Meta.Basic","Lean.Meta.PPGoal"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L463-L464","name":"Lean.Elab.getInfoTrees","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.getInfoTrees","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L460-L461","name":"Lean.Elab.enableInfoTree","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.enableInfoTree","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L448-L458","name":"Lean.Elab.withInfoHole","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.withInfoHole","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L440-L446","name":"Lean.Elab.withMacroExpansionInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.withMacroExpansionInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L435-L437","name":"Lean.Elab.assignInfoHoleId","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.assignInfoHoleId","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L432-L433","name":"Lean.Elab.getInfoHoleIdAssignment?","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.getInfoHoleIdAssignment?","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L420-L430","name":"Lean.Elab.withSaveInfoContext","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.withSaveInfoContext","doc":"Resets the trees state `t₀`, runs `x` to produce a new trees\nstate `t₁` and sets the state to be `t₀ ++ (InfoTree.context Γ <$> t₁)`\nwhere `Γ` is the context derived from the monad state. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L414-L415","name":"Lean.Elab.withInfoContext","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.withInfoContext","doc":"Run `x` as a new child infotree node with header given by `mkInfo`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L403-L411","name":"Lean.Elab.withInfoTreeContext","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.withInfoTreeContext","doc":"Saves the current list of trees `t₀`, runs `x` to produce a new tree list `t₁` and\nruns `mkInfoTree t₁` to get `n : InfoTree` and then restores the trees to be `t₀ ++ [n]`."},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L386-L399","name":"Lean.Elab.withInfoContext'","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.withInfoContext'","doc":"Use this to descend a node on the infotree that is being built.\n\nIt saves the current list of trees `t₀` and resets it and then runs `x >>= mkInfo`, producing either an `i : Info` or a hole id.\nRunning `x >>= mkInfo` will modify the trees state and produce a new list of trees `t₁`.\nIn the `i : Info` case, `t₁` become the children of a node `node i t₁` that is appended to `t₀`.\n "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L373-L378","name":"Lean.Elab.resolveGlobalConstWithInfos","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.resolveGlobalConstWithInfos","doc":"Similar to resolveGlobalConstNoOverloadWithInfo, except if there are multiple name resolutions then it returns them as a list. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L365-L370","name":"Lean.Elab.resolveGlobalConstNoOverloadWithInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.resolveGlobalConstNoOverloadWithInfo","doc":"This does the same job as resolveGlobalConstNoOverload; resolving an identifier\nsyntax to a unique fully resolved name or throwing if there are ambiguities.\nBut also adds this resolved name to the infotree. This means that when you hover\nover a name in the sourcefile you will see the fully resolved name in the hover info."},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L358-L359","name":"Lean.Elab.addCompletionInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.addCompletionInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L354-L356","name":"Lean.Elab.pushInfoLeaf","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.pushInfoLeaf","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L350-L352","name":"Lean.Elab.pushInfoTree","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.pushInfoTree","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L345-L348","name":"Lean.Elab.getResetInfoTrees","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.getResetInfoTrees","doc":"Returns the current array of InfoTrees and resets it to an empty array. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L324-L336","name":"Lean.Elab.InfoTree.format","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.InfoTree.format","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L320-L322","name":"Lean.Elab.Info.updateContext?","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.Info.updateContext?","doc":"Helper function for propagating the tactic metavariable context to its children nodes.\n  We need this function because we preserve `TacticInfo` nodes during backtracking *and* their\n  children. Moreover, we backtrack the metavariable context to undo metavariable assignments.\n  `TacticInfo` nodes save the metavariable context before/after the tactic application, and\n  can be pretty printed without any extra information. This is not the case for `TermInfo` nodes.\n  Without this function, the formatting method would often fail when processing `TermInfo` nodes\n  that are children of `TacticInfo` nodes that have been preserved during backtracking.\n  Saving the metavariable context at `TermInfo` nodes is also not a good option because\n  at `TermInfo` creation time, the metavariable context often miss information, e.g.,\n  a TC problem has not been resolved, a postponed subterm has not been elaborated, etc.\n\n  See `Term.SavedState.restore`.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L297-L304","name":"Lean.Elab.Info.toElabInfo?","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.Info.toElabInfo?","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L288-L295","name":"Lean.Elab.Info.format","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.Info.format","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L283-L286","name":"Lean.Elab.MacroExpansionInfo.format","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.MacroExpansionInfo.format","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L276-L281","name":"Lean.Elab.TacticInfo.format","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.TacticInfo.format","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L270-L274","name":"Lean.Elab.ContextInfo.ppGoals","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.ContextInfo.ppGoals","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L266-L268","name":"Lean.Elab.FieldInfo.format","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.FieldInfo.format","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L263-L264","name":"Lean.Elab.CommandInfo.format","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.CommandInfo.format","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L257-L261","name":"Lean.Elab.CompletionInfo.format","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.CompletionInfo.format","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L249-L255","name":"Lean.Elab.TermInfo.format","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.TermInfo.format","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L246-L247","name":"Lean.Elab.TermInfo.runMetaM","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.TermInfo.runMetaM","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L227-L228","name":"Lean.Elab.ContextInfo.ppSyntax","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.ContextInfo.ppSyntax","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L223-L225","name":"Lean.Elab.ContextInfo.toPPContext","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.ContextInfo.toPPContext","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L212-L221","name":"Lean.Elab.ContextInfo.runMetaM","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.ContextInfo.runMetaM","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L204-L210","name":"Lean.Elab.InfoTree.substitute","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.InfoTree.substitute","doc":"Instantiate the holes on the given `tree` with the assignment table.\n(analoguous to instantiating the metavariables in an expression) "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L198-L200","name":"Lean.Elab.instMonadInfoTree","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.instMonadInfoTree","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L192-L194","name":"Lean.Elab.MonadInfoTree","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.MonadInfoTree","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L190-L190","name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedInfoState","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.instInhabitedInfoState","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L183-L190","name":"Lean.Elab.InfoState","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.InfoState","doc":"This structure is the state that is being used to build an InfoTree object.\nDuring elaboration, some parts of the info tree may be `holes` which need to be filled later.\nThe `assignments` field is used to assign these holes.\nThe `trees` field is a list of pending child trees for the infotree node currently being built.\n\nYou should not need to use `InfoState` directly, instead infotrees should be built with the help of the methods here\nsuch as `pushInfoLeaf` to create leaf nodes and `withInfoContext` to create a nested child node.\n\nTo see how `trees` is used, look at the function body of `withInfoContext'`.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L163-L171","name":"Lean.Elab.InfoTree.findInfo?","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.InfoTree.findInfo?","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L161-L161","name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedInfoTree","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.instInhabitedInfoTree","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L154-L161","name":"Lean.Elab.InfoTree","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.InfoTree","doc":"The InfoTree is a structure that is generated during elaboration and used\n    by the language server to look up information about objects at particular points\n    in the Lean document. For example, tactic information and expected type information in\n    the infoview and information about completions.\n\n    The infotree consists of nodes which may have child nodes. Each node\n    has an `Info` object that contains details about what kind of information\n    is present. Each `Info` object also contains a `Syntax` instance, this is used to\n    map positions in the Lean document to particular info objects.\n\n    An example of a function that extracts information from an infotree for a given\n    position is `InfoTree.goalsAt?` which finds `TacticInfo`.\n\n    Information concerning expressions requires that a context also be saved.\n    `context` nodes store a local context that is used to process expressions\n    in nodes below.\n\n    Because the info tree is generated during elaboration, some parts of the infotree\n    for a particular piece of syntax may not be ready yet. Hence InfoTree supports metavariable-like\n    `hole`s which are filled in later in the same way that unassigned metavariables are.\n"},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L131-L131","name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.instInhabitedInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L123-L131","name":"Lean.Elab.Info","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.Info","doc":"Header information for a node in `InfoTree`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L120-L120","name":"Lean.Elab.instToFormatCustomInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.instToFormatCustomInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L117-L118","name":"Lean.Elab.CustomInfo.format","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.CustomInfo.format","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L115-L115","name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedCustomInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.instInhabitedCustomInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L112-L115","name":"Lean.Elab.CustomInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.CustomInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L110-L110","name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedMacroExpansionInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.instInhabitedMacroExpansionInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L106-L110","name":"Lean.Elab.MacroExpansionInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.MacroExpansionInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L104-L104","name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedTacticInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.instInhabitedTacticInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L99-L104","name":"Lean.Elab.TacticInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.TacticInfo","doc":"The information needed to render the tactic state in the infoview.\n\n    We store the list of goals before and after the execution of a tactic.\n    We also store the metavariable context at each time since we want metavariables\n    unassigned at tactic execution time to be displayed as `?m...`. "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L92-L92","name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedFieldInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.instInhabitedFieldInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L84-L92","name":"Lean.Elab.FieldInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.FieldInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L76-L82","name":"Lean.Elab.CompletionInfo.stx","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.CompletionInfo.stx","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L67-L73","name":"Lean.Elab.CompletionInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.CompletionInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L65-L65","name":"Lean.Elab.instInhabitedCommandInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.instInhabitedCommandInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a1830883843/src/Lean/Elab/InfoTree.lean#L64-L65","name":"Lean.Elab.CommandInfo","docLink":"./Lean/Elab/InfoTree.html#Lean.Elab.CommandInfo","doc":""},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/6a767a66a13c588cce3829bf1de00a183088384